metadata.name: CoolPunks #1
metadata.description: CoolPunks NFT is a collection of 4,444 randomly generated and stylistically curated NFTs that exist on the Ethereum Blockchain. CoolPunks were inspired by two of the largest nft collections, however we are not just a derivative project, we are a derivative with a difference. Holders get exclusive access to airdrops, community voting and giveaways. Visit coolpunksnft.com for more. (Disclaimer: we are not affiliated with Cool Cars or Larva Labs in anyway).
